      },
      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Heart of Might",
        "Client": "Fugen the Elder",
        "Description": "Hey, Squirt. We got some of the\r\nmightiest elder dragons out in the\r\nInfernal Springs. Are they too mighty\r\nfor ya to brawl with? Only one way\r\nto find out. Take \u0027em down and I\u0027ll\r\ngive ya some new titles. Sound\r\ngood? Good! Now go get to it!",
        "Target": "Slay all target monsters",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "C\u0153ur puissant",
        "Client": "Fugen l\u0027Ancien",
        "Description": "H\u00E9, microbe ! De redoutables\r\ndragons anciens se trouvent aux\r\nSources infernales. Tu te sens\r\nd\u0027attaque ou pas ? Si tu r\u00E9ussis\r\n\u00E0 les vaincre, je te refilerai\r\nde nouveaux titres. \u00C7a te va ?\r\nAllez, zou !",
        "Target": "Tuer tous les monstres",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Cuore di potere",
        "Client": "Fugen l\u0027anziano",
        "Description": "Ehi, giovane. Ci sono alcuni\r\ndei draghi anziani pi\u00F9 feroci\r\nalle Sorgenti infernali. Sono\r\ntroppo tosti per te? C\u0027\u00E8 solo\r\nun modo per scoprirlo.\r\nSconfiggili e ti dar\u00F2 dei nuovi\r\ntitoli. Che ne dici? Ora vai!",
        "Target": "Uccidi tutti i mostri assegnati",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Herz der Macht",
        "Client": "Fogen der \u00C4lteste",
        "Description": "Hey Frischling. In den H\u00F6llen-\r\nquellen sind m\u00E4chtige Drachen-\r\n\u00E4lteste. Zu m\u00E4chtig f\u00FCr dich?\r\nGibt nur einen Weg, es rauszu-\r\nfinden. Besiege sie, dann geb\r\nich dir neue Titel. Klingt\r\ngut? Gut, dann los!",
        "Target": "Erlege alle Zielmonster.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Coraz\u00F3n de poder",
        "Client": "Fugen el anciano",
        "Description": "Ey, chico. En la Fuente infernal\r\nhay algunos de los dragones\r\nancianos m\u00E1s terribles jam\u00E1s\r\nvistos. \u00A1Solo hay una forma de\r\naveriguar si son demasiado para\r\nti! V\u00E9ncelos y te dar\u00E9 alg\u00FAn\r\nt\u00EDtulo nuevo. \u00BFHace? \u00A1Al turr\u00F3n!",
        "Target": "Abate a todos los objetivos",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u0421\u0435\u0440\u0434\u0446\u0435 \u0441\u0438\u043B\u044B",
        "Client": "\u0421\u0442\u0430\u0440\u0435\u0439\u0448\u0438\u043D\u0430 \u0424\u0443\u0433\u044D\u043D",
        "Description": "\u042D\u0439, \u0412\u044B\u0441\u043A\u043E\u0447\u043A\u0430! \u0423 \u043D\u0430\u0441 \u0432 \u0410\u0434\u0441\u043A\u0438\u0445\r\n\u0440\u0443\u0447\u044C\u044F\u0445 \u0437\u0430\u0432\u0435\u043B\u0438\u0441\u044C \u043E\u0447\u0435\u043D\u044C \u0441\u0438\u043B\u044C\u043D\u044B\u0435\r\n\u0434\u0440\u0435\u0432\u043D\u0438\u0435 \u0434\u0440\u0430\u043A\u043E\u043D\u044B. \u041C\u043E\u0436\u0435\u0448\u044C\r\n\u0441 \u043D\u0438\u043C\u0438 \u0441\u043F\u0440\u0430\u0432\u0438\u0442\u044C\u0441\u044F? \u041F\u043E\u0440\u0430\r\n\u043F\u0440\u043E\u0432\u0435\u0440\u0438\u0442\u044C. \u041F\u043E\u0431\u0435\u0434\u0438\u0448\u044C \u0438\u0445 \u2014 \u044F \u0434\u0430\u043C\r\n\u0442\u0435\u0431\u0435 \u043D\u043E\u0432\u044B\u0435 \u0442\u0438\u0442\u0443\u043B\u044B. \u0427\u0442\u043E\r\n\u0441\u043A\u0430\u0436\u0435\u0448\u044C? \u041E\u0442\u043B\u0438\u0447\u043D\u043E! \u0412\u043F\u0435\u0440\u0435\u0434!",
        "Target": "\u0423\u0431\u0438\u0442\u044C \u0432\u0441\u0435\u0445 \u0443\u043A\u0430\u0437\u0430\u043D\u043D\u044B\u0445 \u043C\u043E\u043D\u0441\u0442\u0440\u043E\u0432",
        "Fail": "\u0421\u0447\u0435\u0442\u0447\u0438\u043A \u043D\u0430\u0433\u0440\u0430\u0434\u044B \u0434\u043E\u0445\u043E\u0434\u0438\u0442 \u0434\u043E 0\r\n\u0438\u043B\u0438 \u0438\u0441\u0442\u0435\u043A\u0430\u0435\u0442 \u0432\u0440\u0435\u043C\u044F"
